statements: SELECT * FROM TherapeuticInterventions;
SELECT intervention_id, intervention_name, intervention_type FROM TherapeuticInterventions;
SELECT intervention_id, intervention_name, intervention_type, effectiveness_score FROM TherapeuticInterventions WHERE intervention_type = 'Medication';
SELECT intervention_name, effectiveness_score FROM TherapeuticInterventions WHERE outcome_measurements->'success_rate' > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM TherapeuticInterventions ORDER BY intervention_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM TherapeuticInterventions WHERE intervention_type = 'Medication' ORDER BY intervention_name ASC;
SELECT intervention_name, effectiveness_score FROM TherapeuticInterventions WHERE effectiveness_score > 0.7;
SELECT intervention_id, intervention_name, intervention_type FROM TherapeuticInterventions WHERE intervention_id BETWEEN 100 AND 200;
SELECT intervention_id, intervention_name, outcome_measurements FROM TherapeuticInterventions WHERE outcome_measurements->>'primary_goal' = 'Pain Management';
SELECT intervention_name, intervention_type, ROUND(effectiveness_score, 2) AS rounded_score FROM TherapeuticInterventions ORDER BY effectiveness_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM Patients WHERE age > 30
SELECT name, age FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY age DESC
SELECT patient_id, diagnosis FROM Patients WHERE age <= 20
SELECT * FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY name
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Patients
SELECT * FROM Patients WHERE age > 50 ORDER BY name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT diagnosis, name, gender FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT intervention_name, efficacy_rating FROM Interventions WHERE cost < 500 ORDER BY efficacy_rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM Patients p JOIN Interventions i ON p.age = i.efficacy_rating WHERE p.gender = 'Female';
SELECT DISTINCT gender FROM Patients WHERE age BETWEEN 30 AND 40 AND gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM interventions ORDER BY intervention_name DESC;
SELECT intervention_name, intervention_type FROM interventions WHERE effectiveness_score > 0.5;
SELECT patient_name, gender FROM patients WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT intervention_name, intervention_type, effectiveness_score FROM interventions WHERE effectiveness_score < 0.3;
SELECT DISTINCT outcome_type FROM outcomes;
SELECT * FROM interventions WHERE intervention_type = 'Medication' ORDER BY effectiveness_score DESC;
SELECT patient_name, date_of_birth, gender FROM patients WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY date_of_birth ASC;

SELECT patient_name, intervention_name, outcome_measure FROM patients p JOIN interventions i ON p.intervention_id = i.id JOIN outcomes o ON p.patient_id = o.patient_id WHERE intervention_type = 'Therapy' AND outcome_type = 'Improvement' ORDER BY outcome_measure DESC;
SELECT intervention_name, AVG(effectiveness_score) AS avg_score FROM interventions GROUP BY intervention_name HAVING AVG(effectiveness_score) > 7;

SELECT patient_name, outcome_measure FROM patients JOIN outcomes ON patients.patient_id = outcomes.patient_id WHERE intervention_id = 2 AND measurement_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY outcome_measure DESC LIMIT 5;
